---
permalink: /tags/
layout: layouts/home.njk
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Tags
  order: 3
---
<h1>The Tags</h1>
<p>Every topic covered on this blog. Larger tags are more frequent — pick one to see related posts.</p>

{% set cloud = collections.all | tagCloudData %}
<ul class="tag-cloud" aria-label="All tags, sized by post count">
{%- for tag in cloud %}
	<li>
		<a href="/tags/{{ tag.name | slugify }}/" class="tag-cloud-item" style="--weight: {{ tag.weight }}">
			<span class="tag-cloud-name">{{ tag.name }}</span>
			<span class="tag-cloud-count" aria-label="{{ tag.count }} post{% if tag.count != 1 %}s{% endif %}">{{ tag.count }}</span>
		</a>
	</li>
{%- endfor %}
</ul>
